  "phone": "911234567",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Mayor",
    "number": "1",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### 2.2 Crear cliente — CIF duplicado en la misma compañía (409 Conflict)
POST {{baseUrl}}/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Otra García S.L.",
  "cif": "B98765432",
  "email": "otra@constructora.es",
  "phone": "912222222",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Menor",
    "number": "2",
    "postal": "28013",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### 2.3 Crear cliente — datos inválidos (400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "cif": "no-es-un-cif"
}

###

### 2.4 Listar todos los clientes (paginación por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2.5 Listar clientes — paginación explícita
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2.6 Listar clientes — filtro por nombre (búsqueda parcial)
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?name=García
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2.7 Listar clientes — ordenación por fecha de creación descendente
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2.8 Obtener cliente concreto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

